9) For Selecting Specific columns fire Below Query
Select firstname,lastname from employee;

+-----------+----------+
| firstname | lastname |
+-----------+----------+
| amir      | shaikh   |
| adnan     | shaikh   |
| ahmed     | khan     |
+-----------+----------+


